{"type": "article", "id": 26182, "title": "羊角形咖啡杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-29T07:23:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 119, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145452hRQPBNIy6LtiAqYD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这不是号角，而是由 <a href=\"http://www.goat-story.com/\">Anze Miklavec</a> 设计的一款名为 GOAT STORY 的咖啡杯。之所以选择山羊角形状，也有它的渊源——根据传说，一位牧羊人发现他的山羊吃了一种植物的种子之后变得非常兴奋，继而发现了咖啡。如果不想拿着杯子，只要将把手卸下倒置放在平面上，就能把杯子支撑起来了。不仅趣味十足，也兼备了实用性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145448Im6ezXY1gWpJQxFn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145449SE5V9dkWenac1psL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145450bq0ySRskiWJYFxpo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145451H4qmtYcsJOpnI87P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}